{"reviews":[{"name":"Katy","location":"Airbnb Guest","rating":5,"date":"1 day ago","text":"We enjoyed the hot tub and our kids loved the air hockey table! Keep in mind if you are a large group there is not a dish washer and the washing machine is very small. They also ask that water usage be kept to a minimum as it is not connected to city water. We were very grateful they allowed pets with an extra fee. Michael was very quick to respond and super kind!","avatar":"K"},{"name":"Jasmine","location":"5 years on Airbnb","rating":5,"date":"1 week ago","text":"Michael was a great host. We had some unexpected travel changes and he was accommodating to that. He was friendly and helpful with anything we needed! Cabin is in a great spot right off the hwy but far enough tucked away with great views. Great place overall 😊","avatar":"J"},{"name":"Mike","location":"Boyd, Texas","rating":5,"date":"3 weeks ago","text":"beautiful place, just far enough away from town to feel lost in the woods . peaceful.","avatar":"M"},{"name":"Brianna","location":"Montgomery, Texas","rating":5,"date":"January 2026","text":"Beautiful location our family loved it","avatar":"B"},{"name":"Daniel","location":"Midland, Texas","rating":5,"date":"December 2025","text":"Perfect place to get out of the snow and enjoy the views! We loved everything about this home. Even with the snow, 4x4 let us easily access the home and we couldn't have had a better experience. A must stay for Pagosa Springs!","avatar":"D"},{"name":"Martin","location":"Santa Fe, New Mexico","rating":5,"date":"December 2025","text":"The cabin was the perfect spot for all of my family from out of town to relax after a day of skiing and hot springs, plenty of space for everyone. Thanks for having us!","avatar":"M"},{"name":"Clayton","location":"Albuquerque, New Mexico","rating":5,"date":"December 2025","text":"Great cabin! Recommend for your pagosa stay!","avatar":"C"},{"name":"Georgiana","location":"2 months on Airbnb","rating":5,"date":"December 2025","text":"I loved spending Christmas at this peaceful cabin. I loved the hot tub and fire pit.","avatar":"G"},{"name":"Michelle","location":"Albuquerque, New Mexico","rating":5,"date":"November 2025","text":"The cabin was big and beautiful. We had a lovely Thanksgiving there. Everything we needed was available and the house was clean and ideal for a family getaway in the mountains.","avatar":"M"},{"name":"Miguel","location":"2 years on Airbnb","rating":5,"date":"November 2025","text":"Beautiful & homey! 10/10 recommend","avatar":"M"},{"name":"Prateek","location":"McKinney, Texas","rating":5,"date":"October 2025","text":"House is amazing and kids enjoyed a lot. Location is so scenic and amazing. Everything was well maintained making stay comfortable. Stargazing can be done from the property. Highly recommend this place to anyone looking for a beautiful, well equipped stay surrounded by nature. We could see deer family too.","avatar":"P"},{"name":"Adrionna","location":"Flora Vista, New Mexico","rating":5,"date":"October 2025","text":"This was the perfect stay for myself and my husband to unwind and get away after our wedding. It was a peaceful getaway, still within driving distance to town. Would recommend and stay at again!","avatar":"A"}],"pagination":{"page":1,"totalPages":9,"totalReviews":103,"reviewsPerPage":12,"start":1,"end":12,"hasNext":true,"hasPrev":false}}